message: PP3V3_S5 @ C3550 0v..... Hmm.... Let's think about that. What component generates your 3v and 5v rails?

title: [SOLVED] 820-3435 macbook air, green light , not turns on
message:
Before replacing U7501 make sure you are getting 8.5v on pin 23 and 3.42v on pin 12.

If that is the case, then check resistance to ground on PP5V_S5.

If resistance to ground on PP5V_S5 is high enough to not be considered a short circuit to ground, replace U7501.

Do not touch Q7560.
